projects.name: DriveHub - Online Vehicle Rentals Website
projects.description: DriveHub simplifies vehicle rentals with intuitive interfaces and efficient workflows. Users easily browse, reserve, and manage bookings, improving efficiency by 40% for quicker, convenient transactions. Deployed modern web technologies to enhance user engagement by 30%, and introduced real-time availability tracking, leading to a 20% increase in customer satisfaction and a 15% reduction in cart abandonment. Leveraged modern web technologies for a responsive, user-friendly interface, increasing interaction and accessibility across devices, enhancing platform usability.

projects.name: Imports and Exports Analysis in India using Python
projects.description: Analyzed Indias export and import data using Python, uncovering key trade patterns that led to a 15% improvement in supply chain efficiency and informed strategic decision-making. Generated statistical summaries and visualizations to enhance comprehension and interpretation of Indias trade dynamics, providing clear insights into import and export patterns for informed decision-making. Provided concise, data-driven insights to support strategic decision-making related to Indias import and export activities, enhancing understanding of trade patterns and facilitating informed policy decisions.

projects.name: Hotel Management System using Abstract Window Toolkit
projects.description: Developed a user-friendly graphical interface using Abstract Window Toolkit (AWT) to handle hotel booking operations. Facilitated seamless hotel room bookings for customers, increasing booking efficiency by 40%. Streamlined management of room availability and customer details, reducing manual entry errors by 30%.

experiences.company_name: Andhra Pradesh State Skill Development Corporation
experiences.description: Developed a real-time project focused on Imports and Exports Analysis in India using Python. Discovered patterns unique to Indias trade data by summarizing datasets with visualizations and statistical analysis, and gaining expertise in Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) principles and procedures. Created a solid data analysis project by utilizing Python libraries for data manipulation, plotting, statistical visualizations, and numerical operations, including Numpy, Pandas, Matplotlib, and Seaborn.
